    <text xml:lang="it">
        <body>
            <div type="diary">
                <pb n="136" facs="#p136" />
                <ab>
                    <s>
                        <lb n="1" facs="#p136_l1" break="yes" />
                        fino alla base di <persName ref="#Lu">Luigi</persName><pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Arrivano i Tedeschi
                        <lb n="2" facs="#p136_l2" break="yes" />
                        e gli altri lo lasciano sulla porta<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Si sente
                        <lb n="3" facs="#p136_l3" break="yes" />
                        svenire<pc>,</pc> ma fa uno sforzo e si nasconde
                        <lb n="4" facs="#p136_l4" break="yes" />
                        sotto il letto<pc>.</pc> Quando entravano i Tedeschi
                        <lb n="5" facs="#p136_l5" break="yes" />
                        aveva ancora le scarpe fuori<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Un capitano
                        <lb n="6" facs="#p136_l6" break="yes" />
                        e un tenente fanno il loro quartiere generale
                        <lb n="7" facs="#p136_l7" break="yes" />
                        per 3 ore<pc>:</pc> <del rend="overstrike">Se s</del> ricevono notizie<pc>;</pc> impartiscono
                        <lb n="8" facs="#p136_l8" break="yes" />
                        ordini<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Poi partono dopo avere incendiato
                        <lb n="9" facs="#p136_l9" break="yes" />
                        la paglia<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Sotto la paglia c'è un fumo d'in<pc type="syllabication">-</pc>
                        <lb n="10" facs="#p136_l10" break="no" />
                        ferno<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        <persName ref="Za">Zama</persName> si morde la lingua per non
                        <lb n="11" facs="#p136_l11" break="yes" />
                        tossire<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Quando <del rend="overstrike">non</del> non resiste più e si sente
                        <lb n="12" facs="#p136_l12" break="yes" />
                        soffocare esce con la rivoltella <choice><sic>ni</sic><corr resp="#LP">in</corr></choice> pugno<pc>,</pc>
                        <lb n="13" facs="#p136_l13" break="yes" />
                        senza sapere se i <choice><abbr type="suspension">Ted</abbr><expan resp="#LP">Ted<ex>eschi</ex></expan></choice> sono già lontani<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        La
                        <lb n="14" facs="#p136_l14" break="yes" />
                        neve <add resp="#EA" place="above">dei tetti</add> si scioglie al calore e l'acqua scende
                        <lb n="15" facs="#p136_l15" break="yes" />
                        a catinelle<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        I <choice><abbr type="suspension">Ted</abbr><expan resp="#LP">Ted<ex>eschi</ex></expan></choice> si stanno allontanando<pc>,</pc>
                        <lb n="16" facs="#p136_l16" break="yes" />
                        ma sono appena usciti<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Recupera una coperta
                        <lb n="17" facs="#p136_l17" break="yes" />
                        bruciacchiata e ripara nella grangia vicina<pc>,</pc>
                        <lb n="18" facs="#p136_l18" break="yes" />
                        dove si ferma altre 3 ore<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Poi sente passare
                        <lb n="19" facs="#p136_l19" break="yes" />
                        uno vicino e chiama aiuto<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Lo portano
                        <lb n="20" facs="#p136_l20" break="yes" />
                        <choice><sic>ni</sic><corr resp="#LP">in</corr></choice> un posto più riparato<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        <persName ref="Gi">Gina</persName>, credendo che
                        <lb n="21" facs="#p136_l21" break="yes" />
                        stesse per morire e per evitare che i Tedeschi
                        <lb n="22" facs="#p136_l22" break="yes" />
                        lo prendano gli fa 3 iniezioni di morfina
                        <lb n="23" facs="#p136_l23" break="yes" />
                        per ucciderlo<pc>,</pc> ma riesce a superare anche
                        <lb n="24" facs="#p136_l24" break="yes" />
                        questa prova<pc>.</pc> 
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Per 4 volte in un giorno sfiora la
                        <lb n="25" facs="#p136_l25" break="yes" />
                        morte<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                </ab>
                <pb n="137" facs="#p137" />
                <ab>
                    <lb facs="p137_date" break="yes" />
                    <date when="1944-01-26">26 <choice><abbr type="suspension">genn<pc>.</pc></abbr><expan resp="#LP">genn<ex>aio</ex></expan></choice></date>
                    <s>
                        <lb n="1" facs="#p137_l1" break="yes" />
                        Le vicende di ieri non ebbi ieri sera tempo di
                        <lb n="2" facs="#p137_l2" break="yes" />
                        narrarle con precisione<pc>;</pc> bisogna che le riferisca
                        <lb n="3" facs="#p137_l3" break="yes" />
                        ora<pc>,</pc> specie un<del rend="overstrike"><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"></gap></del> colloquio con un giovane studente di
                        <lb n="4" facs="#p137_l4" break="yes" />
                        medicina<pc>,</pc> che ha voluto incontrarsi con me e che ci
                        <lb n="5" facs="#p137_l5" break="yes" />
                        aiuterà molto<pc>:</pc> porterà messaggi e pacchi da e a <placeName ref="#TO">To<pc type="syllabication">-</pc>
                        <lb n="6" facs="#p137_l6" break="no" />
                        rino</placeName><pc>,</pc> ritirerà malati nella sua casa e li curerà<pc>,</pc>
                        <lb n="7" facs="#p137_l7" break="yes" />
                        ci <del rend="overstrike">dara</del> procurerà 30 moschetti<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Non è poco<pc>,</pc> ma
                        <lb n="8" facs="#p137_l8" break="yes" />
                        quando gli ho <choice><sic>chieso</sic><corr resp="#LP">chiesto</corr></choice> le sue opinioni politiche<pc>,</pc> mi
                        <lb n="9" facs="#p137_l9" break="yes" />
                        ha risposto<pc>:</pc> non ne ho<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Allora gli ho ripetuto quanto
                        <lb n="10" facs="#p137_l10" break="yes" />
                        da due settimane vado ripetendo a tutti i miei
                        <lb n="11" facs="#p137_l11" break="yes" />
                        uomini<pc>:</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        <seg xml:id="trs01">
                            <del rend="overstrike">se non hai opinioni po</del> il Fascismo non
                            <lb n="14" facs="#p137_l12" break="yes" />
                            è una tegola cadutaci per caso sulla testa<pc>;</pc> è
                            <lb n="15" facs="#p137_l13" break="yes" />
                            un<del rend="ovestrike"><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"></gap></del> effetto della apoliticità e quindi della
                            <lb n="16" facs="#p137_l14" break="yes" />
                            immoralità civile del Popolo italiano<pc>.</pc>
                            Se non
                            <lb n="17" facs="#p137_l15" break="yes" />
                            ci facciamo una <del>cultura politica<pc>,</pc> ricadrete</del> co<pc type="syllabication">-</pc>
                            <lb n="18" facs="#p137_l16" break="no" />
                            scienza politica<pc>,</pc> non sapremo governarci e un
                            <lb n="19" facs="#p137_l17" break="yes" />
                            popolo che non sa governarsi cade necessaria<pc type="syllabication">-</pc>
                            <lb n="20" facs="#p137_l18" break="no" />
                            mente sotto il dominio straniero o sotto la
                            <lb n="21" facs="#p137_l19" break="yes" />
                            dittatura di uno dei suoi<pc>.</pc>
                            <del>Non ci avevi</del>
                            <lb n="22" facs="#p137_l20" break="yes" />
                        </seg>
                        <seg xml:id="trs02">
                            <metamark function="transposition" place="margin-left" rend="line"></metamark>
                            Un giovane russo o americano della tua età
                            <lb n="12" facs="#p137_l21" break="yes" />
                            <del rend="overstrike"><gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"></gap></del> non mi risponderebbe certo come te<pc>.</pc>
                            <del rend="overstrike">Non ci</del>
                            <lb n="13" facs="#p137_l22" break="yes" />
                        </seg>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Ho ragione<pc>?</pc> Si ha ammesso<pc>.</pc> <pc>-</pc> E non ci avevi
                        <lb n="23" facs="#p137_l23" break="yes" />
                        mai pensato<pc>?</pc> <del rend="overstrike">Come</del> <del rend="overstrike">Come crede</del> <add resp="#EA" place="above">Ti pare</add> che uno come me
                        <lb n="24" facs="#p137_l24" break="yes" />
                        pensi a queste cose<pc>?</pc> Ma mi ha promesso di occu<pc type="syllabication">-</pc>
                        <lb n="25" facs="#p137_l25" break="no" />
                        parsi seriamente di queste cose<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        <lb n="26" facs="#p137_l26" break="yes" />
                        Più <del rend="overstrike">grave</del> <add resp="#EA" place="above">penoso</add> è stato il colloquio con i <add resp="#EA" place="above">2</add> <persName><choice><abbr type="suspension">P</abbr><expan resp="#LP">P<ex>altrinieri</ex></expan></choice></persName><pc>.</pc> e con
                        <lb n="27" facs="#p137_l27" break="yes" />
                        <persName ref="#Ser"><choice><abbr type="suspension">S</abbr><expan resp="#LP">S<ex>ergio</ex></expan></choice></persName><pc>.</pc> ieri pomeriggio<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Come avevo scritto in uno
                        <lb n="28" facs="#p137_l28" break="yes" />
                        dei fogli distrutti<pc>,</pc> <persName ref="#Ser"><choice><abbr type="suspension">S</abbr><expan resp="#LP">S<ex>ergio</ex></expan></choice></persName><pc>,</pc> <del rend="overstrike">fermato da me</del> <del rend="overstrike">presento</del>
                        <lb n="29" facs="#p137_l29" break="yes" />
                        quando fummo presentati e seppe che ero <choice><abbr type="suspension">comm</abbr><expan resp="#LP">commm<ex>issario</ex></expan></choice>
                        <lb n="30" facs="#p137_l30" break="yes" />
                        disse ridendo<pc>:</pc> ma noi non li vogliamo i politici
                        <lb n="31" facs="#p137_l31" break="yes" />
                        e <del rend="overstrike">tutto</del> durante la conversazione tutti e tre con<pc type="syllabication">-</pc>
                        <lb n="32" facs="#p137_l32" break="yes" />
                        tinuavano a ridere scioccamente<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Domani il
                        <lb n="33" facs="#p137_l33" break="yes" />
                        colonnello e io vedremo <persName ref="Ser">Sergio</persName><pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Gli diremo
                        <lb n="34" facs="#p137_l34" break="yes" />
                        chiaramente<pc>:</pc> il <orgName ref="#FN"><choice><abbr type="suspension">Fr<pc>.</pc></abbr><expan resp="#LP">Fr<ex>onte</ex></expan></choice> <choice><abbr type="suspension">Naz<pc>.</pc></abbr><expan resp="#LP">Naz<ex>ionale</ex></expan></choice></orgName> non riconosce gli
                    </s>
                </ab>
                <pb n="138" facs="#p138" />
                <ab>
                    <s>
                        <lb n="1" facs="#p138_l1" break="yes" />
                        azzurri: se tu sei azzurro, non puoi stare con noi<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        <lb n="2" facs="#p138_l2" break="yes" />
                        Dici di essere apolitico, ma invece sei ba<choice><sic>u</sic><corr resp="#LP"></corr></choice>dogliano<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        <lb n="3" facs="#p138_l3" break="yes" />
                        D'altra parte persuaditi che sei indietro di 40
                        <lb n="4" facs="#p138_l4" break="yes" />
                        anni<pc>:</pc> democrazia e comunismo<pc>:</pc> questo è l'avve<pc type="syllabication">-</pc>
                        <lb n="5" facs="#p138_l5" break="no" />
                        nire del mondo<pc>:</pc> per le monarchie e i militaristi
                        <lb n="6" facs="#p138_l6" break="yes" />
                        non c'è posto<pc>.</pc><pc>&raquo;</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        <del rend="overstrike">Qua</del> Gli operai<pc>,</pc> spinti dal biso<pc type="syllabication">-</pc>
                        <lb n="7" facs="#p138_l7" break="no" />
                        gno<pc>,</pc> si sono occupati <choice><sic>ni</sic><corr resp="#LP">in</corr></choice> questi anni di problemi
                        <lb n="8" facs="#p138_l8" break="yes" />
                        politici e hanno maturato<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Questi sciocchi gio<pc type="syllabication">-</pc>
                        <lb n="9" facs="#p138_l9" break="no" />
                        vani borghesi non hanno mai avuto <del rend="bisogno">bisogno</del> lo
                        <lb n="10" facs="#p138_l10" break="yes" />
                        sprone di occuparsi di nulla<pc>,</pc> ma<pc>,</pc> come studenti<pc>,</pc>
                        <lb n="11" facs="#p138_l11" break="yes" />
                        come classe colta<pc>,</pc> sono anzi stati aperti alla
                        <lb n="12" facs="#p138_l12" break="yes" />
                        <del rend="overstrike">indifferenza fasc</del> propaganda fascista e <del rend="overstrike">par<pc type="syllabication">-</pc></del>
                        <lb n="13" facs="#p138_l13" break="yes" />
                        <del rend="overstrike">to</del> il vuoto di questa riempiè tutto il loro vuoto
                        <lb n="14" facs="#p138_l14" break="yes" />
                        intellettualmente pigri e moralmente scettici<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        <lb n="15" facs="#p138_l15" break="yes" />
                        <pc>-</pc> Noi <pc>-</pc> diceva uno del ieri <pc>-</pc> siamo degli
                        <lb n="16" facs="#p138_l16" break="yes" />
                        sportivi <pc>-</pc> cioè<pc>,</pc> <choice><sic>ni</sic><corr resp="#LP">in</corr></choice> altre parole<pc>,</pc> preferiamo stancare
                        <lb n="17" facs="#p138_l17" break="yes" />
                        le gambe che la testa<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Non so qual filosofo ha
                        <lb n="18" facs="#p138_l18" break="yes" />
                        osservato che nessuna fatica è grave come
                        <lb n="19" facs="#p138_l19" break="yes" />
                        quella di pensare e questi ragazzi<pc>,</pc> senza essere
                        <lb n="20" facs="#p138_l20" break="yes" />
                        filosofi<pc>,</pc> conoscono perfettamente il saggio afo<pc type="syllabication">-</pc>
                        <lb n="21" facs="#p138_l21" break="no" />
                        risma<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Siamo di fronte a quello che in termini
                        <lb n="22" facs="#p138_l22" break="yes" />
                        marxisti si chiama fine di una classe economica<pc>.</pc>
                        <lb n="23" facs="#p138_l23" break="yes" />
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        <seg xml:id="trs03">
                            <metamark function="transposition" place="margin-left" rend="line"></metamark>
                            <c xml:id="toLower">S</c>ervitù ai propri ordini<pc>,</pc>
                        </seg>
                        <seg xml:id="trs04">
                            <c xml:id="toUpper">t</c>itoli di studi <del rend="overstrike">rag</del>
                            <lb n="24" facs="#p138_l24" break="yes" />
                            ottenuti senza merito<pc>,</pc> divertimenti e donne<pc>,</pc>
                            <lb n="25" facs="#p138_l25" break="yes" />
                        </seg>
                        guerra intesa sportivamente <add resp="#EA" place="below">perché sono indisciplinati</add> sono i tratti ca<pc type="syllabication">-</pc>
                        <lb n="26" facs="#p138_l26" break="yes" />
                        ratteristici di questi giovani<pc>,</pc> che<pc>,</pc> senza accor<pc>-</pc>
                        <lb n="27" facs="#p138_l27" break="no" />
                        gersene<pc>,</pc> corrono verso la propria rovina<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Se lo
                        <lb n="28" facs="#p138_l28" break="yes" />
                        capissero<pc>,</pc> ma hanno il cervello atrofizzato<pc>,</pc> si
                        <lb n="29" facs="#p138_l29" break="yes" />
                        getterebbero nei partiti di destra o nel <orgName ref="#PdA"><choice><abbr type="initial">P<pc>.</pc> d<pc>.</pc> A<pc>.</pc></abbr><expan resp="#LP">Partito d'Azione</expan></choice></orgName>
                        <lb n="30" facs="#p138_l30" break="yes" />
                        per salvare i propri capitali<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        Invece<pc>,</pc> quando noi
                        <lb n="31" facs="#p138_l31" break="yes" />
                        parliamo loro<pc>,</pc> ridono allegramente<pc>:</pc> di chi<pc>?</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        <lb n="32" facs="#p138_l32" break="yes" />
                        Di se stessi o di noi<pc>:</pc> non si capisce bene<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
                    <s>
                        <lb n="33" facs="#p138_l33" break="yes" />
                        <del rend="overstrike"><gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"></gap></del> <del rend="overstrike">Con la decadenza</del> La religione è la forma
                        <lb n="34" facs="#p138_l34" break="yes" />
                        più facile ed elementare di vita dello spirito<pc>;</pc>
                        <lb n="35" facs="#p138_l35" break="yes" />
                        con la <del rend="overstrike">decad</del> fine della religione nella società
                        <lb n="36" facs="#p138_l36" break="yes" />
                        borghese<pc>,</pc> <del rend="overstrike">questi g</del> a molti non è più rimasto
                        <lb n="37" facs="#p138_l37" break="yes" />
                        nulla<pc>:</pc> si è tolto il passato senza sostituirlo con
                        <lb n="38" facs="#p138_l38" break="yes" />
                        altro<pc>.</pc>
                    </s>
